|<span data-ttu-id="19d40-110">Object []-Parser</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="19d40-110">Object[] pArr</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="19d40-111">ErrorWrapper [10] von ErrorWrapper (77)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="19d40-111">ErrorWrapper[10] of ErrorWrapper(77)</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="19d40-112">`VARIANT[10]` von `VT_ERROR`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="19d40-112">`VARIANT[10]` of `VT_ERROR`</span></span>|  
